datasets.name: dataset_9
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', First_Device_Event_Date_Time) AS Month_First_Device_Event_Date_Time, MEASURE(Active_Devices) AS Active_Devices, MEASURE(Active_Devices) / SUM(MEASURE(Active_Devices)) OVER (PARTITION BY First_Device_Event_Date_Time) AS Percent_Devices_Returning, Months_Since_First_Use AS Months_Since_First_Use, Session_Type AS Session_Type, Weeks_Since_First_Use AS Weeks_Since_First_Use FROM HPX_Retention_CSS_Analytics WHERE First_Device_Event_Date_Time >= '2023-05-01' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', First_Device_Event_Date_Time), Months_Since_First_Use, Session_Type, Weeks_Since_First_Use ORDER BY Month_First_Device_Event_Date_Time
